Do I need to purchase anything? What tool/software/program do I need?
1-No Money required
2-Download Visaul Studio Code to make the coding easier to craete and read, but you can use any program or just the terminal if you know your way arround.
3-Install Python and required plugins
  -Install python3    latest version (I used version 3.8.9)
  -install nornir:    pip3 install nornir (I used version 3.1.1)
  -Install plugins:   These are all my installed plugins, however you will only need Netmiko,utils (List of nornir plugins: https://nornir.tech/nornir/plugins/)
    cesaranaya@MacBook-Pro-8 NornirTest % pip3 freeze | grep nornir
